The wholesale price for custom address stamps are $35 each, plus a one time bulk shipping fee of $30. You may charge whatever you wish for the custom stamps in your shop. 
You are sent a physical sample of a custom stamp (of your shops information), an stamp example sheet, a paper pastries pen, and 10 order forms. 
Once you get the display, you are ready to sell stamps in your shop. The customer chooses a stamp, fills out a form and walks away with a copy, you keep the original. 
They have the option to have their custom stamp shipped directly to them, or to the shop for pickup. You either scan the form, take a photo of it, or type it up and email me the info. 
I then send a proof directly to the client. After it's been approved, the stamp will ship within a week.
